15 year 2500 player. When you walk around there are so many young faces
playing for so mmany strong teams.} 6. cxd5 c5 7. dxc5 Nd7 8. e3 O-O 9. Bc4
Nxc5 10. Nge2 Qb6 11. Qd2 Bf5 $146 {This novelty looks like a natural move but
